Serge Perathoner kɛna Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa tʊ nɛ palʊla-ɩ mɩsɩkʊm fenaɣ kɩyakʊ 27 wiye pɩnaɣ 1953. Ɛkɛna wendu luɖu nɛ ti-teyu, soo mabʊ taa lɛ ɛkɛ nesi ;ɖɩdamɩyɛ tʊ, ɛñɔɔzʊʊ nɛ eɖiyu wendu teya lalaa. Ɛlaba tʊma nɛ wendu teya sɔsaɣa ɛzɩ: Yves Simon, Michel Berger, Luc Plamondon, France Gall, Johnny Hallyday, Sylvie Vartan, Céline Dion…Ɛñɔɔzʊʊ mba palakɩ amʊza nɛ tanaʊ yaa films cinéma et télévision yɔ, ɛzɩ Starmania nɛ Notre-Dame de Paris ɛnʊ sɩŋnana-wɛ pɛ-tɛ Hendu ñɔɔzʊʊ taa. Serge Perathner laba e-sukuli kɛ Paarii tɛtʊ taa ɖenɖe pawɩlʊ nesi tɛɛ tʊma, amʊʊza nɛ hendu teu yɔ. Peeɖe lɛ ɛkpɛlɩka piyano, eluki wendu nɛ ɛmaɣ-tʊ nɛ ɛñɔɔzʊʊ ɖɔɖɔ wendu ndʊ tɩɩwɛɛ yɔ nɛ ɛɖaanʊʊ-tʊ teu. Ɛna mba peteɣ hendu yɔ pɔɖɔɔ pɩdɩɩfɛyɩ nɛ pa-taa kɔyɔ: France Gall, Michel Berger, Johnny Hallyday, Sylvie Vartan, Jane Birkin, Gérard Manset… Céline Dion nɛ France Gall palɩza hendu lɛ, ɛnʊ ñɔɔzɩna-wɛ tʊ.
